"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-23-clarke-upbeat-ahead-olympics-debut\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"STUTTGART, Germany - Having clocked a season's best time at the London Diamond League on Saturday, World Championships 400m hurdles finalist Roshawn Clarke says he is rounding into form at the right time.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\", \"score\": 0.6256917206827279, \"rank\": 0.5982297569768841, \"text\": \"STUTTGART\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\"}, {\"begin\": 11, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9932317307805427, \"rank\": 0.006576266691619825, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 64, \"end\": 70, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_GAA\", \"score\": 0.6628971438586572, \"rank\": 0.5085290378234333, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_GAA\"}, {\"begin\": 71, \"end\": 85, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999864888851416, \"rank\": 1.2219624723102301e-05, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the 20-year-old is feeling very upbeat and confident ahead of this week's start of the Olympic Games in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 314, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996446359268, \"rank\": 3.5536412455889617e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke, the national record holder in the event, recorded 47.63 seconds to finish second in London.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 421, \"end\": 427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_GAA\", \"score\": 0.6628971438586572, \"rank\": 0.5085290378234333, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_GAA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is the second-fastest Jamaican and the seventh-fastest man globally this year.\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Malik James-King, who defeated Clarke in the final at the JAAA/Puma National Senior Championships last month, is the fastest Jamaican and fifth-fastest in the world this year with his time of 47.42 seconds.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 512, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\", \"score\": 0.9841643591817397, \"rank\": 0.012213259951012885, \"text\": \"Malik\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke, set to compete at the Olympic Games for the first time, said he has been improving on his technique a lot this season and is very optimistic about his chances of a podium finish at the championships.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 927, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Running fast at this point of the season is no surprise to me because I am where I want to be.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Running 47.63 now, I can not complain,\\\" said Clarke.\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I ran 47.36 last year at the national championships and I am three times better now than last year with my technique and everything.\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I would also say that I am ahead of my time right now and I know that I am peaking at the right time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke, a former Camperdown High School standout, will be aiming to break the country's 20-year medal drought in the event.\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camperdown_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.5959938651144819, \"rank\": 0.6765577189964392, \"text\": \"Camperdown\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camperdown_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camperdown_railway_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Danny McFarlane, who claimed silver at the 2004 Games in Athens, Greece, is the last Jamaican to have won a medal in the event at the Olympics  Coached by Okeile Stewart at Swept Track club, Clarke pointed out that he has gained a lot of experience from competing at his first World Athletics Championships in Budapest, Hungary, in 2023, and is determined to do extremely well in Paris.\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_McFarlane\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Danny McFarlane\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_McFarlane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_McFarlane\"}, {\"begin\": 1502, \"end\": 1508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999996865690755, \"rank\": 3.134309502012929e-07, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1510, \"end\": 1516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997740302440368, \"rank\": 0.00022601469155720836, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9999969846849112, \"rank\": 3.0152559586540812e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}, {\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.7106921849449853, \"rank\": 0.40707720101809797, \"text\": \"Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\"}, {\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.7541111860034748, \"rank\": 0.32606440305703865, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 1765, \"end\": 1772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9499429081089299, \"rank\": 0.052681684908672366, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1825, \"end\": 1830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996446359268, \"rank\": 3.5536412455889617e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My confidence level is always high because I know what I can do.\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it does not matter who is in the race or which lane I am running in, I know that I am just going there to do my best for myself and my country.\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I also know that my experience from the world championships last year can get me very far in my event in Paris.\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2154, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996446359268, \"rank\": 3.5536412455889617e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mentally, I am going in very strong knowing that I can come out of this championship with something to my name.\\\"\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also noted that he is not putting himself under any undue pressure as he is just looking to produce his best efforts whenever he steps out on the track.\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not nervous at all but I am just excited to run because I am going to treat this just like a regular meet like the World [Athletics] Championships.\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They [rivals] are running fast and I am also running fast because I am now seventh in the world rankings, so I am not too far back.\\\"\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2737, \"entities\": []}]}"